data.description: Back On The Market As Buyer Could Not Perform Subject To Complete Cancellation of Current Escrow.  Come Live The Dream in Desert Hot Springs!  This Home is very spacious and comfortable for most any family.  It Has 3 Bedrooms and 2 Baths, with a 2 Car Attached Garage and a Laundry Room.  There is a nice size backyard, Which Includes a Two year old Shed.   It Is a Short Trip Into Palm Springs and Joshua Tree National Park.  Come Enjoy The Beauty of The Desert With This Home.
